<lb n="0864c09" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0864008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說持句神呪<note n="0864009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（亦云陀羅尼句）【三】</note><note n="0864009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，經亦云陀羅尼句【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864009"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">經亦云陀羅尼句</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0864c10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0864c11" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">吳月支優婆塞支<note n="0864010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謙＋（拾遺編入第一）【宋】</note><note n="0864010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謙【大】，謙拾遺編入第一【宋】</note><app n="0864010"><lem wit="【大】">謙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">謙拾遺編入第一</rdg></app>譯</byline>
<lb n="0864c12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0864c1201">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT21p0864c1204" cb:place="inline">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，與
<lb n="0864c13" ed="T"/>大比丘眾千二百五十人，菩薩萬人。爾時從
<lb n="0864c14" ed="T"/>是佛土過億<note n="0864011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">百千＝千百【三】＊</note><note n="0864011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">百千【大】＊，千百【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0864011"><lem wit="【大】">百千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">千百</rdg></app>佛國，有世界<note n="0864012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＋（曰）【三】＊</note><note n="0864012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】＊，名曰【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0864012"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">名曰</rdg></app>無量華，
<lb n="0864c15" ed="T"/>其佛號<note n="0864013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鄧＝燈【明】＊</note><note n="0864013" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->鄧【大】＊，燈【明】＊</note><app n="0864013"><lem wit="【大】">鄧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">燈</rdg></app>尊王如來無所著至真等正覺，今
<lb n="0864c16" ed="T"/>現在說法。<note n="0864014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（時）＋彼【三】</note><note n="0864014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彼【大】，時彼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864014"><lem wit="【大】">彼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">時彼</rdg></app>佛遣二菩薩，一名無量光明、二
<lb n="0864c17" ed="T"/>名大光明。時二菩薩來至釋迦文佛所，稽首
<lb n="0864c18" ed="T"/>佛足，却住一面，<note n="0864015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔前〕－【宋】</note><note n="0864015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0864015"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>白佛言：「唯然世尊！從<note n="0864016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【三】</note><note n="0864016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，此【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864016"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">此</rdg></app>
<lb n="0864c19" ed="T"/>佛土過億<app type="star" corresp="#0864011"><lem wit="【大】">百千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">千百</rdg></app>佛國，有世界<app type="star" corresp="#0864012"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">名曰</rdg></app>無量華，其
<lb n="0864c20" ed="T"/>佛號鄧尊王如來，遣我等來。<note n="0864017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如何）＋世【宋】</note><note n="0864017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世【大】，如何世【宋】</note><app n="0864017"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">如何世</rdg></app>尊如<note n="0864018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（平）＋常【三】</note><note n="0864018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，平常【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864018"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">平常</rdg></app>不？
<lb n="0864c21" ed="T"/>其眾安隱無他耶？天、龍、鬼神、餓鬼、<note n="0864019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">女鬼鳩桓＝鳩洹鬼【三】</note><note n="0864019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">女鬼鳩桓【大】，鳩洹鬼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864019"><lem wit="【大】">女鬼、鳩桓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">鳩洹鬼</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0864c22" ed="T"/>若人非人、虎狼毒<note n="0864020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">獸＝狩【宋】</note><note n="0864020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">獸【大】，狩【宋】</note><app n="0864020"><lem wit="【大】">獸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">狩</rdg></app>，得無嬈亂人民？用是故
<lb n="0864c23" ed="T"/><note n="0864021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（彼）＋佛【三】</note><note n="0864021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，彼佛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864021"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">彼佛</rdg></app>遣是持句呪來，哀念眾生<note n="0864022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令＝全【三】</note><note n="0864022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，全【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864022"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">全</rdg></app>安吉善，名
<lb n="0864c24" ed="T"/>聞威神<note n="0864023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝德【宋】</note><note n="0864023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得【大】，德【宋】</note><app n="0864023"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">德</rdg></app>力如是。</p>
<lb n="0864c25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0864c2501" cb:type="dharani">「闍梨摩訶　闍梨羅尼　優佉目佉　沙<note n="0864024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【三】＊</note><note n="0864024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波【大】＊，婆【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0864024"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">婆</rdg></app>
<lb n="0864c26" ed="T"/>提　摩訶沙<app type="star" corresp="#0864024"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">婆</rdg></app>提」</p>
<lb n="0864c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0864c2701">佛告阿難：「受是持句呪，執持誦說。佛世難值，
<lb n="0864c28" ed="T"/>持句呪亦為難<note n="0864025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遇＋（佛語阿難若）【三】</note><note n="0864025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遇【大】，遇佛語阿難若【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864025"><lem wit="【大】">遇</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">遇佛語阿難若</rdg></app>。善男子善女人受<note n="0864026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是持＝持是【三】</note><note n="0864026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是持【大】，持是【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0864026"><lem wit="【大】">是持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">持是</rdg></app>
<lb n="0864c29" ed="T"/>句呪，諷誦讀，識七世宿命。受持者一切浮陀
<pb n="0865a" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1351.0865a"/>
<lb n="0865a01" ed="T"/>鬼神、若<note n="0865001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人非＝非人【明】</note><note n="0865001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人非【大】，非人【明】</note><app n="0865001"><lem wit="【大】">人非</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">非人</rdg></app>人不得嬈近，毒蛇不<note n="0865002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敢＝能【三】</note><note n="0865002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">敢【大】，能【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865002"><lem wit="【大】">敢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">能</rdg></app>螫、毒
<lb n="0865a02" ed="T"/>藥自然除、刀亦不能傷、王亦不能害、梵亦
<lb n="0865a03" ed="T"/><note n="0865003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（能）【三】</note><note n="0865003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不【大】，不能【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865003"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">不能</rdg></app>瞋之。是<note n="0865004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（受）＋持【三】</note><note n="0865004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持【大】，受持【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865004"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">受持</rdg></app>句呪，七十七億佛所說，犯是
<lb n="0865a04" ed="T"/>呪者當獲重罪。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0865a0407" cb:place="inline">復有菩薩彌勒等八十人，告
<lb n="0865a05" ed="T"/>賢者阿難：「我亦當說持句呪，哀念眾生，令
<lb n="0865a06" ed="T"/><note n="0865005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">安＝其【宋】</note><note n="0865005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">安【大】，其【宋】</note><app n="0865005"><lem wit="【大】">安</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">其</rdg></app>吉善，名聞威神得力如是。</p>
<lb n="0865a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0865a0701" cb:type="dharani">「阿知和知　吒佉羅羅　里彌喜利　彌利提
<lb n="0865a08" ed="T"/>盧　留彌勒」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0865a0805" cb:place="inline">佛告阿難：「受是持句呪，執<note n="0865006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＝治【宋】</note><note n="0865006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持【大】，治【宋】</note><app n="0865006"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">治</rdg></app>
<lb n="0865a09" ed="T"/>誦說。佛世難值，持句呪諷誦讀，識十四世宿
<lb n="0865a10" ed="T"/>命。受持者一切浮陀鬼神、若人非人不得嬈
<lb n="0865a11" ed="T"/>近，毒蛇不<note n="0865007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敢＝能【明】</note><note n="0865007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">敢【大】，能【明】</note><app n="0865007"><lem wit="【大】">敢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">能</rdg></app>螫、毒藥自然除、刀亦不能傷、
<lb n="0865a12" ed="T"/>王亦不敢害、梵亦不瞋之。是持句呪，八十四
<lb n="0865a13" ed="T"/>億佛所說，謗是呪者當獲重罪。」</p>
<lb n="0865a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0865a1401">佛告阿難：「我亦當說持句呪，哀念眾生令安
<lb n="0865a15" ed="T"/>吉，善名聞威神得力如是。</p>
<lb n="0865a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0865a1601" cb:type="dharani">「阿知和知　那知鳩那知　提梨　沙羅波提
<lb n="0865a17" ed="T"/>　阿那波提　波那提　波那迦和尼　摩訶
<lb n="0865a18" ed="T"/>迦和尼」</p>
<lb n="0865a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0865a1901">佛告阿難：「受是持句呪，執持誦說。佛世難值，
<lb n="0865a20" ed="T"/>持句呪亦為難遇。善男子善女人受是持句
<lb n="0865a21" ed="T"/>呪諷誦讀，識無數世宿命。受持者一切浮陀
<lb n="0865a22" ed="T"/>鬼神、若人非人不敢嬈近，毒蛇不敢螫、毒藥
<lb n="0865a23" ed="T"/>自然除、刀亦不敢傷、王亦不敢害、梵亦不瞋
<lb n="0865a24" ed="T"/>之。是持句呪，無數億佛所說，犯是呪者當獲
<lb n="0865a25" ed="T"/>重罪。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0865a2503" cb:place="inline">佛告阿難：「是持句呪，行道中當念之。若
<lb n="0865a26" ed="T"/>至縣官、若行賊中、若蠱道若、毒若刀刃中、若
<lb n="0865a27" ed="T"/>人非人中當念之。是持句呪於枯樹令生<note n="0865008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">葉＝草【宋】【元】</note><note n="0865008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">葉【大】，草【宋】【元】</note><app n="0865008"><lem wit="【大】">葉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">草</rdg></app>
<lb n="0865a28" ed="T"/>華實，何況為人結縷也，當使<note n="0865009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吉＋（善）【元】【明】</note><note n="0865009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吉【大】，吉善【元】【明】</note><app n="0865009"><lem wit="【大】">吉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">吉善</rdg></app>，百病消除，
<lb n="0865a29" ed="T"/>自然安隱，辟除凶害。南無佛，令呪<note n="0865010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝比【宋】，所【元】【明】</note><note n="0865010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆【大】，比【宋】，所【元】【明】</note><app n="0865010"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">比</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">所</rdg></app>得從願。」</p>
<pb n="0865b" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1351.0865b"/>
<lb n="0865b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0865b0101">佛說經已，皆大歡喜。</p>
<lb n="0865b02" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說持句神呪經</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
